Overview


This firm, formerly The Equitable Companies, Inc., provides a range of financial products including insurance, annuities, and mutual funds.  The firm also offers a variety of financial, investment advisory and planning services through AXA Advisors, LLC.  The Equitable Life Assurance Society is a subsidiary.

 








